Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"幸福大家庭"前情提要...\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Previously on "One Big Happy"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.47,0:00:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里举行的婚礼都是不合法的\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}None of the weddings that happened here were legal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的签证一周后就到期了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}My visa expires in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在那时之前我们不能结婚 我就会被遣送回英格兰\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}If we're not married by then, I'll be exiled back to England.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.87,0:00:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我不会让这件事发生的\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Well, I'm not gonna let that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.04,0:00:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们再结一次婚好了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}We'll just get married again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.41,0:00:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在机场接到了你的父亲\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I flew your father in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他不是我父亲 - 我是她的丈夫\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}- That's not my father. - I'm her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 什么?  - 我没听错?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}- Excuse me? - I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马丁 我没爱过你\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I never loved you, Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是利用你\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I was only using you to get out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来摆脱我当时在家里的尴尬处境\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}of a bad situation at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然我怎么会认识你3天\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Why else would I marry you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就嫁给你呢？\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}after only knowing you for three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 让我解释  - 没什么好解释的\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}- Just let me explain. - There's nothing to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你嫁给了你遇见的第一个混球\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}You marry the first sucker you meet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来解决你的问题\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}to solve your problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你嫁给我是不是因为你要被驱逐出境呢?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Did you marry me because you were about to be deported?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 马丁走了   - 卢克也走了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}- Martin's gone. - So is Luke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.98,0:00:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 现在只有你和我了吧\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}So, what you're saying is it's just you and me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.17,0:00:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利兹 非常感谢你能让我和你睡\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Lizzy, thank you so much for letting me sleep with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:00:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我醒的时候你就已经在我旁边了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I woke up, and you were next to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.38,0:00:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其说是让 不如说是你突然袭击\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}so that's more of an assault than a "Letting."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.73,0:01:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是... 没有卢克\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I just... I can't sleep in that bed another night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我晚上睡不着觉\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}without Luke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教教我如何面对孤独\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Teach me how to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你之前从来没一个人睡过\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}So, wait, you've never slept alone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这听起来跟你这胸也有自己的重力吸引一样扯\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}It's like they have their own gravitational pull.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.51,0:01:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 我好想卢克\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}God, I miss Luke so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.71,0:01:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想念他的味道 还有他的抚摸\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I miss his smell, I miss his touch,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.95,0:01:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他亲吻我身体每个部位并和它们说晚安的方式\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}the way he kisses every single part of my body good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.35,0:01:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他得花一个半小时的时间\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}It takes him an hour and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真的很甜蜜\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}But it's so sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.90,0:01:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是怀孕的缘故 但是我突然间真的恶心了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}It might be the pregnancy, but suddenly I'm nauseous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我主要还是想念他的诗了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}But most of all I miss his poetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.22,0:01:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗? 我非常确定卢克唯一知道的诗就是\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Poetry? I'm pretty sure the only poem Luke knows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"啤酒之前喝白酒 忧愁疾病不再有"\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}is "Beer before liquor never been sicker."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:01:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是  每晚他都会在纸上写一句话\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}No. Every night he'd write one word on a note,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.37,0:01:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后放在我的枕头上\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}and then he'd place it on my pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样在周末 就汇成了一首诗\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}And then at the end of the week, it'd be a poem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.71,0:01:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"心在纠缠\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}"Hearts intertwined,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜蜜香唇叫我性欲大发"\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}soft kisses move my junk."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利兹 如果我俩明天不能结婚\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Lizzy, if he and I aren't married by tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.72,0:02:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就被遣送回国了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'll be deported...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样就没人来让他性欲大发了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Then he won't have anyone to move his junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普鲁登斯 卢克知道你的签证要到期了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Prudence, Luke knows that your visa is about to expire,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他真的对你很失望\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}but he's really upset with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.15,0:02:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且理由很充分\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}and for good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不像你从中间挤牙膏\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}It's not like you squeezed the toothpaste from the middle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是用他的剃刀修理你的那个地方\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}or used his razor on your hoo-ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没那么做过  你瞧?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'd never do that. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你说的\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'll take your word for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 说真的\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}But, seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么之前不告诉卢克你结过婚呢？\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}why didn't you tell Luke that you were married before?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.01,0:02:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能怪他不再信任我了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}And I can't blame him for not trusting me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是难道你没有过一个秘密\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}But haven't you ever had a secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得它让你感到很羞愧吗\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}like something you were ashamed of,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你并不需要要保守秘密\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}that you didn't need to keep a secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你这么做了因为你害怕\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}but you did because you were afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别的人会怎么想你?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}of what people might think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个倒确实打动我了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}That resonates with me, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保守了一个18年的大秘密\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I kept a pretty big secret for 18 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 14年\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Well, 14.
