Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你不介意\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}And you said you were fine
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且会照顾好小鱼罗德尼的\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}and you would take care of Rodney Dangerfish
