Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托 我只是有一次忘了喂它\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Come on, I forgot to feed him one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 一次? - 几次吧\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}- One time? - A few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:08:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 真的吗? - 好吧 每一次\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}- Really? - Okay, every single time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是本来应该是我在那个舞蹈夏令营的\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}But it should've been me at that dance camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又不能做这个 还有这个\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}You can't do this or this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者这个\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Or this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 你真是人见人爱的开心果啊\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yeah, you're a gosh-damn delight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 上帝 我杀了你的鱼\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, my God, I killed your fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许卢克是对的\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}And maybe Luke is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许在某种程度上 我是破坏了他和普鲁登斯\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Maybe on some level, I sabotaged him and Prudence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鱼罗德尼的鬼魂也同意\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}The ghost of Rodney Dangerfish agrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真糟糕\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我只有四个小时来搞定这些\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}And I only have like four hours to fix this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则普鲁登斯就要永远消失了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}or Prudence is gone for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果他都不想和她说话 我能做什么呢?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}But what can I do if he won't even talk to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 好吧\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我疯狂爱上罗伊那会儿\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}When I get really mad at Roy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我首先想到的是我一开始为什么\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I just remember why I fell in love with him
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会爱上他...\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该知道的\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}You should know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚给了我灵感\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}And you just gave me an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要做的就是让卢克和普鲁登斯在同一个房间\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}All I need to do is get Luke and Prudence in the same room
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重现他们坠入爱河的场景\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}and recreate the moment they fell in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记起来了!\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他让我怀孕了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}He got me pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说 警官学校是很严\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I mean the police academy was hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们有这个\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}But we had this one guy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.47,0:09:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能用嘴发出各种音效的家伙\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}who made fun sound effects with his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的警官之路也从此拜拜了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}His career kind of dropped off after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卢克 跟他们讲讲FBI那档事儿\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Luke, tell them about the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 那时有个小气鬼\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, there was this one real meany.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个执法专业术语\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}That's a law enforcement term.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的名字是汉尼拔 莱克特(著名食人杀人狂)\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}His name was Hannibal Lector.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.55,0:09:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 天哪 他们还以他为原型拍了部电影呢\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, my God, they made a movie about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.79,0:09:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见过他?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}You met him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是塔吉特一个小收银员\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm just a cashier at Target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是个百货商店\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}It's like a store
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那儿你能买到鞋子\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}where you can buy shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦片粥 文胸 户外家具\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}and cereal and bras and outdoor furniture
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包装纸 还有...\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}and wrapping paper and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去过塔吉特 嘉琪\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I've been to Target, Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 你们知道么 我兄弟卢克不单单是个FBI特工\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Well, you know my man, Luke, is not only an FBI agent,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还会写淫诗\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}he also writes sensual poetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就爱诗\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I love poetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马雅 安琪罗(作家名)妥妥是我的菜啊\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Maya Angelou is like... my girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我读一首你的诗吧\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Do me one of your poems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一会儿再读 我得去嘘嘘\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Do it later, 'cause I have to pee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 嘉琪 我们去嘘嘘\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Come on, Jackie, let's go pee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是得去个嘘嘘了 我们去嘘嘘吧\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I totally have to pee. Let's go pee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托 老兄 起来嗨\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Come on, man, perk up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得让这叽叽喳喳的女孩儿开心\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Please just keep the squeaky one entertained.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想助我一柱擎天了吗?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Do you not want me to have sex?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讲真的 我是在是不关心\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Honestly, I have like zero investment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真没什么兴趣\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm just not into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我遇见普鲁登斯的地方\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I met Prudence here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她当时就站在吧台后边\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}She was standing right behind that bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我一生中最棒的一个晚上了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Best night of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我要放弃这一切了吗?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Am I supposed to just give all that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就几个小时而已\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Just for like a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女厕所总是人满为患\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}The line was too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们就在外面嘘嘘了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}We peed outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利兹 你要带我去哪儿?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Lizzy, where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:10:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我就好\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Just trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 这是我跟卢克第一次相遇的酒吧\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Wait, this is the bar where Luke and I first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一见钟情\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}It was love at first sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我一生中最棒的一晚了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Best night of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天咱就来把昨日重现\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Well, we're about to deja vu that bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普鲁登斯?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Prudence?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卢克!\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Luke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不敢相信你在这儿 就像...\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I can't believe you're here, this is just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那晚我们初次...\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}The night we first...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你们俩现在所经历的\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I think what you two are experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全是破坏者的相反版本\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}is the opposite of sabotage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 我一直没跟你说...\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm so sorry that I never told you about...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卢克 我们要走啦\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Luke, we're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是跟我聊过天的男人里\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}And you're like the hottest guy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最火辣的了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}who's ever talked to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定要跟我上床\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}so you're definitely gonna get me to do stuff.
