Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你跟她在一起了 - 没有\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}- You're with her. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我现在就摸着他的小屁屁呢\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yes, I'm touching his butt right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为你哭了整整两天\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I spent two days crying over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给你发了我大咪咪的特写\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I sent you glamour shots of my no-no bits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你却跟别人搞上了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}And you're with another girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给她写淫诗?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}writing her poems?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她刚刚尿在外面了 那可不是我喜欢的!\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}She just peed outside, that is not my thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还不是而已啦\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 嘉琪!\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Shut up, Jackie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你在塔吉特工作吗?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Wait, do you work at Target?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你这么容易就能开始下一段\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}If it's that easy for you to move on,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就忘了吧\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}just forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也忘了我吧!\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}And forget me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别 普鲁登斯 等等!\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}No, Prudence, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你没事儿吧? - 当然有!\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}- Are you okay? - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利兹 你到底是在干嘛啊?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Lizzie, what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修复关系?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I fixed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普鲁登斯 你这是要干嘛?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Prudence, what are you doing?
