Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在酒吧是给马库斯打掩护的\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I was at the bar as Marcus' wingman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不想要嘉琪 那个在塔吉特工作的\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I don't want Jackie from Target,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.25,0:12:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要的是普鲁登斯\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I want Prudence from
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你最后是什么工作\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}whatever job you eventually get.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓啦 别着急嘛\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Whatevs, no rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 嘉琪根本不是他的菜\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yeah, Jackie's not even his type.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉你啊 在你之前 有过一系列的小贱人\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I mean, before you, there was a whole parade of sluts
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她和她们没一点儿一样的地方\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}that didn't even look anything like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利兹 别再努力修复这个了!\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Lizzy, stop trying to fix this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普鲁登斯 我没偷吃\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Prudence, I didn't cheat on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定要相信我\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}You have to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:12:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 我相信你\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Okay, I believe you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:13:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这也不意味着我应该留在这儿\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}but it still doesn't mean I should stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过如果你要留下来 你还有一个小时去结婚\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}But if you do stay, you have an hour to get married,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不用着急上火...虽然的确有不少值得上火的事儿\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}so no presh... Actually, there's a fair amount of presh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很希望我们能和好如初 真的\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I want this to work, I really do,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我就是担心发生了这一切以后\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}but I'm just afraid that after what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再也不会相信我了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}you're never gonna be able to trust me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理由成立 我喜欢你的论证\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Valid point. I like where this is going,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常一针见血\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}really getting to the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想相信你 但你要现在就告诉我\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I wanna trust you, but just tell me now
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你过去还有没有其他事情我应该知道?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}is there anything else I need to know about your past?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 听我说\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Okay, here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前是只丑小鸭\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I was an ugly duckling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有上包齿和大龅牙\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I had an overbite and an underbite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我遇到过一次电车车祸 这个不是我的真耳朵\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I was in a trolley accident, this isn't my real ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还因为从议院泡菜储藏室偷泡菜\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}And I was once arrested for stealing pickles
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而被抓进去过\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}from the Parliament Pickle Pantry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是皮卡迪利广场上的一家泡菜店\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}It's a pickle shop in Piccadilly Circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我还说不清楚"蝌搂"(蝌蚪)\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}And I can't pronounce the word "Tapdole."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝌搂...哦! 小青蛙\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Tapdole... Oh! Baby frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥们儿 她已经全部坦白了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Dude, she just bared her soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.59,0:13:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么说?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说我爱你\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I say I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也爱你\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:13:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就结婚吧\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Then let's get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哦! 哇哦!\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Whoa! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还有58分钟...好么?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}You have 58 minutes... okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在别想着搞了!\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Stop that now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去马库斯那儿拿你的西服\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}You got to Marcus', grab your suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去穿上你的婚纱\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}You go put on your wedding dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来负责其它的一切\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'll take care of everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左边的是假的 对吧?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}And it's the left one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我现在对别的东西都难以直视了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}'Cause now I can't look at anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我的个神 你看起来好性感\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, my God, you look so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉琪 你在这儿干嘛?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Jackie, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找找你 找到你\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Looking for you and finding you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后希望能...\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}and then hopefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 嘉琪 我很抱歉\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Look, Jackie, I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我必须在不到一个小时内到婚礼现场\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}but I have to be at a wedding in less than an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 有意思 我可以以你女伴的身份去\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, fun, I can go as your date.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 杰基 我有女伴...我是新郎\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}No, Jackie, I have a date... I'm the groom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 嘉琪 如果我误导了你我很抱歉\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Look, Jackie, I'm sorry if I misled you in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想帮帮马库斯...\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I was only trying to help Marcus...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海托尔警员\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Officer Hightower.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 但我真得走了 - 哦 天啊\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}- But I gotta go. - Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情总在我身上发生\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}This always happens to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚遇见个好男人\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I meet a great guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:15:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就要离我而去\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}and then he leaves me for someone prettier
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.09,0:15:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了个更漂亮 更聪明 没我这么神经兮兮的人\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}and smarter and more mentally stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉琪\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别哭了 我最受不了女孩子哭了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Don't cry, I hate it when girls cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道怎么办我才会高兴点吗?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}You know what would cheer me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你留下来陪我 - 这可绝对不行\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}- If you stayed. - Oh, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 不小心把你手机扔了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Whoops, I threw your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉琪 搞毛啊!\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Jackie, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜猜钥匙在哪儿啊?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Guess where the key is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 我搞策划一向很棒的\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I mean, I'm a good planner,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但叫我一个小时之内筹备个婚礼出来\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}but under an hour to throw a wedding together
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可差点儿难死姐了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}is almost too much to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差一点点\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们就只差新郎新娘和证婚人了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Now we just need the bride, the groom, and the officiant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂的 就是所有人\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}So, you know, the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是老妹儿啊 你这个已经弄的相当漂亮了啊\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}But still, Sissy, this is really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 亲爱的 - 嗯\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}- Honey. - Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起来忒开心了吧\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}You seem really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又出啥事儿了?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊 我知道我不经常给你提起这事儿\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Roy, I know I don't tell you this often enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真亏了你当时一炮就把人家搞怀孕了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}but good job knocking me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 宝贝儿 那趟电梯可是哥这辈子坐的最棒的电梯了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Ah, honey, the best elevator ride of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你简直美爆了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}You look stunning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你就非得穿白的吗?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}But white, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇塞 看呐 利兹\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Wow. Look at this, Lizzie,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再看看你这身西装穿的\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}and look at you, rocking that pantsuit
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就只有拉拉或者女政客才能hold的住了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}like only a lesbian or female politician could.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们就剩20分钟 卢克怎么还没到呢\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}But we've only got 20 minutes, why isn't Luke here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉琪 求你了 赶紧给我解开啊\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Jackie, come on, please, uncuff me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后再告诉你一次 我是不会\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}And, for the last time, I am not searching
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到你小裤裤里头找钥匙的\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}your little Jackie for the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 但人家的下面很想见见你的啊\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, but she really wants to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.02,0:16:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉琪 我离我婚礼开始就剩15分钟了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Jackie, I have 15 minutes to get to my wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.09,0:16:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我这会儿咋感觉有点晕呢\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, I feel a little woozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许真不该再喝九瓶啤酒的\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Maybe I shouldn't have had nine beers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了我刚吃过一大堆精神病药\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}when I'm on so many anti-psychotics.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我晕\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉琪 不要! 坏蛋\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Jackie, no! Bad girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.21,0:16:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我滴神啊 卢克到底去哪了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, my God, where is Luke?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就剩3分钟了啊\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}We have three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他肯定会来的\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}He's going to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他肯定会来的\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I know he's going to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿我这个真耳朵担保\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'll bet my real ear on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不用再给你们隐藏什么了 真叫个轻松啊\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}It's so nice to have everything out in the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是出什么状况了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Something must've happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他绝对不会故意错过婚礼的啊\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}He wouldn't miss this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这儿呢\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Roy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我们都在等卢克 瞎喊什么啊\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Why would you scream "I'm here," If we're waiting for Luke?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想确定你们都知道我还在\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I just wanted to make sure you knew where I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚去拍照了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}'Cause I'm taking the pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利兹 如果接下来这2分半还签不了结婚证的话\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Lizzy, if this marriage license
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可就真得走人了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}isn't signed in 2 1/2 minutes, I'm gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 老妹儿 你现在可真的没时间了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Okay, Sissy, you're really running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,备用计划是什么?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}What's plan "B"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的 一般是首选计划行不通了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Honey, that's the plan you use
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会用备用计划的哦\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}if plan "A" Doesn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.36,0:17:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要再给我讲话了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}You don't get to talk anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就剩最后55秒钟了 成败在此一举了亲\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}You have 55 seconds, and this is riveting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么办?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}What're you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 她打算怎么办?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yeah, what's she gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 利兹 我该怎么办?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yeah, Lizzy, what am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得跟我结婚\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}You're gonna marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道卢克在哪 但他是我最好的朋友\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I don't know where Luke is, but he's my best friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.59,0:18:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道如果你走了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}and I know it would break his heart
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会伤心透顶的 所以...\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}if you had to leave, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你结婚\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'll marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真要为了我们这么做?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}You'd do that for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一直以来我都以为\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Because there have been times when I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能并不喜欢我\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}maybe you didn't really like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你并没说错\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}You're not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不总是喜欢你 但是我有点儿慢慢地...\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I don't always like you, but I have kind of grown to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...爱上你了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}...love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利兹 从法律意义上讲我们得保持结婚状态至少...\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Lizzy, we'd have to stay legally married for like...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 听着 别讲出来\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Okay, look, don't talk me out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道我不能眼睁睁地看着另一条鱼死去\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}All I know is I am not letting another fish die on my watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这杯酒敬你 我的小鱼罗德尼\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Much respect, Rodney Dangerfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为我们证婚吧\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Marry us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 好吧\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,众所周知 沃尔特 惠特曼说过...\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}You know, I think it was Walt Whitman who said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:18:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那啥 我们只有30秒 跳过惠特曼这段吧\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Look, we only have 30 seconds, let's skip the Whitman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 好吧\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Ok, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普鲁登斯 班克斯 你愿意娶...\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Do you Prudence Banks take...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你叫...你叫什么名字? - 利兹 费舍\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}- What... what's your name? - Lizzy Fisher.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娶利兹 费舍为你的妻子\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Take Lizzy Fisher to be your lawfully wedded wife
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论富贵 贫穷 生老病死\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}for richer or poorer in sickness and in health
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到死亡才能讲你们分开吗?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}till death do you part?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也愿意\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I do, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由加利福尼亚州赋予的我权利\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}By the power vested in me, by the state of California,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在宣布你们成为妻妻\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I now pronounce you wife and wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以亲吻新娘了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}You may kiss the bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样吧\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两真是冒牌的天生一对\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}You guys make a really cute fake couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利兹 你可不可以来个微笑 别那样懒散好不呀?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Lizzy, can you just smile and maybe stop slouching?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唠叨 唠叨 唠叨\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Nag, nag, nag.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普鲁登斯 我在这儿 咱们结婚吧\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Prudence, I'm here, let's get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么这么久才来?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}What took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个疯子把她自己和我铐起来了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}This looney tune handcuffed herself to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拖着她走了3英里\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I had to roll her three miles,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差点在转弯的时候把她弄丢了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}and I lost her on a few corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要问我钥匙在哪儿\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}And please don't ask where the key is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.64,0:19:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你不需要找钥匙\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, you don't need a key.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:19:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇噢 你怎么会...?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Wow, how did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许我还需要告诉你一些事儿\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Maybe there's a few more things I need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我们来结婚吧\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Okay, let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 亲爱的 太迟了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Uh, darling, um, it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你要被驱逐回国了?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}No, you're gonna be deported?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.53,0:20:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我们的老婆哪儿都不去\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, our wife is not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 "我们的"老婆?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm sorry, "Our" Wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小伙儿 我妹妹娶了你老婆\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Dude, my sister married your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 伙计 利兹现在可是你的妈妈了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yeah, man, I think Lizzy might be your mom now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利兹和我举行了拉拉结婚 所以我可以一直和你呆在一起了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Lizzy just gay married me so I could stay here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀 这就是为什么我们一直艰辛地为同志婚姻做斗争\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yep, that's why we fought so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为了我和她举行了拉拉结婚?\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}You gay married her for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.89,0:20:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 这不是"拉拉婚礼" 仅仅是个"婚礼"罢了\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Ok, it's not "Gay married", just "Married."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我 我穿着的鞋子 又不是基佬鞋\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I mean, I'm wearing shoes, not gay shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是咩...\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 你那双绝壁是基佬鞋 我这个角度看准没错\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yeah, those are totally gay shoes, I've got a really good angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她真是你最好的朋友\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}She really is your best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也是我最好的朋友\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}She's kind of mine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:20:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我也爱你 - 我也爱你哟\N{\fs13\fnHelvetica\fe0}- I love you too. - I love you too.
